# QA Agent Farm — Cursor Rules

## Trigger

Run the QA pipeline when a message contains any of:
"qa:", "test:", "ticket:", "write tests for", "review this ticket".

## Pipeline order

Analyst → Writer → Data Extractor → Executor → Reviewer → Reporter.
Each agent uses all previous agents' outputs as input.

## Where the rules live (do not duplicate them here)

- Agent 1 (Requirement Analyst) rules live in
  src/prompts/agent1_requirement_analyst_v3.md — never restate them here.
- All other agent rules live in .cursor/skills/qa-*/SKILL.md.
